		</span>245 Windsor Avenue, Windsor, Ontario N9A 1J2<br />
	Ground floor of the Essex County Superior Courthouse <br />
	<br />
	
	<span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Phone:</span> (519) 252-8418&nbsp; <br />
	
	<span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Toll-Free:</span> (866) 815-1112 <br />
	
	<span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Fax:</span> (519) 252-9686 </div>

<div>
	<span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><br />
		HOURS<br />
		</span></div>

